ss planet is migrating radially outwards in locations\nwhere there is a positive gradient of a pressure bump (zonal flow).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 May 2011 16:15:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-07-19"}
