es such as the\nrise of the counterjet, detailed jet simulations remain indispensable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 May 2011 14:30:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Apr 2012 15:13:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
